    <div class="content-section">
        <h2>Feature Overview</h2>
        <p><strong>Feature:</strong> Add Grok.ai (xAI) support to the Comserv AI Chat system with K8s secrets management, admin model selection, and runtime API key configuration</p>
        <p><strong>Objective:</strong> Enable admins to configure Grok API keys at runtime and users to choose between Ollama (local) and Grok (cloud-based) for AI queries</p>
        <p><strong>Timeline:</strong> Phase 1: ✅ Complete | Phase 2: ✅ Complete | Phase 3: ✅ Complete | Phase 4: Pending (Optional)</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section">
        <h2 id="completed-phases">✅ Completed Phases</h2>

        <h3>Phase 1: Requirements & Specification (COMPLETE)</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>✅ Phase 1.0: Requirements document with 5 user stories</li>
            <li>✅ Phase 1.1: Technical specification with architecture and API contracts</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Phase 2: Core Implementation (COMPLETE - 2026-01-07)</h3>

        <h4>Task 2.1: Create Comserv::Model::Grok ✅ COMPLETE</h4>
        <ul>
            <li>✅ File: <code>Comserv/lib/Comserv/Model/Grok.pm</code> (532 lines)</li>
            <li>✅ Implements all 5 methods: BUILD, query(), chat(), check_connection(), _send_request()</li>
            <li>✅ K8s secrets priority: <code>/run/secrets/grok_api_key</code> → <code>$ENV{GROK_API_KEY}</code></li>
            <li>✅ Error handling: Authentication (401/403), rate limiting (429), service errors (503)</li>
            <li>✅ Multi-turn conversation support with message history</li>
            <li>✅ No API keys exposed in logs or error messages</li>
        </ul>

        <h4>Task 2.2: Modify AI Controller - Provider Routing ✅ COMPLETE</h4>
        <ul>
            <li>✅ File: <code>Comserv/lib/Comserv/Controller/AI.pm</code> (modified, +40 lines)</li>
            <li>✅ Added Grok import at line 26</li>
            <li>✅ Provider parameter extraction from JSON body and form parameters</li>
            <li>✅ Conditional routing (lines 309-407):
                <ul>
                    <li>If <code>provider=grok</code>: Route to Grok model</li>
                    <li>Else (default): Route to Ollama model</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li>✅ Error handling for missing API keys with user-friendly messages</li>
            <li>✅ Backward compatible - existing Ollama functionality unchanged</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

